        <p class="bio-text">My name is Mike Wohl, and I'm arriving at software development from a wide-ranging background in many fields. I have previous experience in music, archaeology, sales, public libraries, technical communication, customer service and support. I'm looking forward to the opportunity to develop new skills in the field of technology, and to seeing what doors those skills open.</p>
